  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK403">
<l>kallā tavaru naṉinallar kaṟṟārmuṟ</l>
<l>collā tirukkap peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The unlearned also are very excellent men, if they know how to keep silence before the learned.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
